data.description: Welcome to the epitome of elegance in the sought-after Hanover Pointe Subdivision! This 2.5-story residence presents an expansive open floor plan, adorned with numerous windows, crown molding, and recessed lighting! The interconnected living room, dining area, and kitchen form the heart of this home, perfect for hosting gatherings. A charming fireplace graces the living room, adding a touch of warmth to the atmosphere. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a sizable kitchen island. Clever storage solutions under the staircase optimize the space while providing convenience. Journey to the second floor, where the primary bedroom awaits with a large walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom offering dual vanities, a scenic soaking tub, and a walk-in shower. Two additional bedrooms on this level provide comfort and versatility. Ascend to the upper level to discover a sizable bonus room, perfect for a home office, theater, or your own private sanctuary. Step outside to the fenced backyard, featuring a patio for delightful outdoor entertainment. With easy access to I-885, this home ensures convenient connections to downtown Durham's vibrant scene, including restaurants, shops, and activities!
